# Checklist Content & Safety Copy

## Content rules

- Each item needs stable `id`, short `label`, optional `hint`
- Merge templates by context flags; dedupe by `id`
- Keep merged lists focused; split into categories if long

## Language

- Assistant for preparation, not a safety authority
- No decompression, gas mix, or medical advice in templates
- Mark unverified items with `[review]` for instructor pass

## Sources

Align with `agents/checklist-content-agent.md` and `docs/research/ux-flow.md`.

Run Security & Safety agent before publishing template changes widely.
